4.57/5  rDev +1.8%look: 4.5 | smell: 5 | taste: 4.5 | feel: 4 |  overall: 4.5Poured on tap at ChurchKey first into a small snifter, then into a tumbler. Vintage 2008. Shared a pint with other BA drabmuh!!
